MATLAB figures are displayed interactively when the scripts run.

To save them to this folder, add the following after each figure() call in the scripts:

  saveas(gcf, fullfile('figures', 'figure_name.png'));

Expected figures:
  fig1_transmitter_spectra.png     — time & frequency domain plots (transmitter.m)
  fig2_rf_filter_output.png        — RF filter output
  fig3_rf_mixer_output.png         — RF mixer output (before IF filter)
  fig4_if_filter_output.png        — IF filter output
  fig5_coherent_demod_output.png   — coherent demodulator output (before LPF)
  fig6_lpf_output.png              — LPF output (recovered baseband)
  fig7_no_rf_mixer_output.png      — RF mixer output without RF filter
  fig8_no_rf_if_filter.png         — IF filter output without RF filter
  fig9_no_rf_demod_output.png      — demodulator output without RF filter
  fig10_no_rf_lpf_output.png       — LPF output without RF filter
